        "-   @echeverriaGreenMobilityWellbeing2022 suggests greener modes of mobility.\n",
        "\n",
        "-   Shop sustainability in Estonia [@lillevaliUuringVastutustundlikkusEesti2022; @EstwatchEstwatchiVarskest]. Tarbimise jalajälg poes [@helensaarmetsTarbimiselSilmagaNahtamatu2021]. Offsets at the point of sale [@GrenpayHeastaOma].\n",
        "\n",
        "-   @GreenFintechTrends2020 report predicts the rise of personalizing sustainable finance, because of its potential to grow customer loyalty, through improving the user experience. Similarly to good design, interacting with sustainable finance for the 'green-minded' demographics, providing a reliable green product is a way to build customer loyalty.\n",
        "\n",
