        "### Towards Tracking Sustainability: Carbon Tracking\n",
        "\n",
        "The founder of the Commons (formerly known as Joro) consumer CO~2e~ tracking app recounts how people have a gut feeling about the 2000 calories one needs to eat daily, so perhaps daily CO~2e~ tracking could develop a gut feeling about one's carbon footprint [@jasonjacobsEpisodeSanchaliPal2019].\n",
        "\n",
