        "\n",
        "-   @dwarkeshpatelMarkZuckerbergLlama2024 META open-sourced the largest language model (70 billion parameters) which with performance rivaling several of the proprietary models.\n",
        "\n",
        "-   Image-generation is now fast it's possible to create images in real-time while the user is typing @dwarkeshpatelMarkZuckerbergLlama2024\n",
